Package: kdevplatform
Section: kde
Architecture: all
Depends: kdevplatform-libs (>= ${source:Version}), kdevplatform-data (>= ${source:Version})
Description: KDevelop framework for KDE4
 This metapackage installs the KDevelop framework.
 .
 This package is part of the KDevelop framework.

Package: kdevplatform-libs
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, libsublime1 (>= ${source:Version})
Description: shared libraries for the KDevelop framework
 This package contains shared libraries needed to run integrated development
 environments based on the KDevelop framework.
 .
 This package is part of the KDevelop framework.

Package: kdevplatform-data
Section: kde
Architecture: all
Description: architecture-independent data for the KDevelop framework
 This package contains architecture-independent data files needed by
 integrated development environments based on the KDevelop framework.
 .
 This package is part of the KDevelop framework.

Package: kdevplatform-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: kdevplatform-libs (= ${binary:Version}), ${sameVersionDep:kdelibs5-dev:kdevplatform-libs}
Description: development files for the KDevelop framework
 This package contains development files for building integrated development
 environments based on the KDevelop framework.
 .
 This package is part of the KDevelop framework.

Package: kdevplatform-dbg
Section: devel
Architecture: any
Priority: extra
Depends: kdevplatform-libs (= ${binary:Version}), kdelibs5-dbg, libc6-dbg [amd64]
Description: debugging symbols for the KDevelop framework
 This package contains the debugging symbols associated with kdevplatform.
 They will automatically be used by gdb for debugging kdevplatform-related
 issues.
 .
 This package is part of the KDevelop framework.

